ptolemy.data.expr

Interface ParseTreeVisitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractParseTreeVisitor, CParseTreeCodeGenerator, ParseTreeDumper, ParseTreeEvaluator, ParseTreeEvaluatorForGuardExpression, ParseTreeFreeVariableCollector, ParseTreeFreeVariableRenamer, ParseTreeSpecializer, ParseTreeTypeInference, ParseTreeWriter

    public interface ParseTreeVisitor
    This class implements the visitor pattern for parse trees in the expression language.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 2.1
    Author:
    Steve Neuendorffer
